---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Cookie Policy - Dental Barcelo Clinic">
  <main class="container mx-auto px-4 py-8 max-w-4xl bg-custom-light">
    <h1 class="text-custom-dark text-3xl font-bold mb-8">Cookie Policy</h1>

    <div class="space-y-6">
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-custom-dark text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">
          1. What are cookies?
        </h2>
        <p class="text-custom-brown">
          Cookies are small text files that are stored on your device when you
          visit our website. These cookies help us make our website work
          properly and improve our services.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-custom-dark text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">
          2. Types of cookies we use
        </h2>
        <p class="text-custom-brown">We use the following types of cookies:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc ml-6 mt-2">
          <li>
            Technical cookies: Necessary for the basic operation of the website
          </li>
          <li>
            Preference cookies: To remember your language preferences and other
            settings
          </li>
          <li>
            Analytics cookies: To improve our services by analyzing how our
            website is used
          </li>
          <li>
            Performance cookies: To measure and improve our website's
            performance
          </li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-custom-dark text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">
          3. Third-party cookies
        </h2>
        <p class="text-custom-brown">
          We use third-party services that may also set cookies on your device:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc ml-6 mt-2">
          <li>Vercel Analytics: To analyze the use of our website</li>
          <li>Vercel Speed Insights: To measure our website's performance</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-custom-dark text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">
          4. Cookie duration
        </h2>
        <p class="text-custom-brown">
          Cookies can remain on your device for different periods of time:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc ml-6 mt-2">
          <li>Session cookies: They are deleted when you close your browser</li>
          <li>
            Persistent cookies: They remain on your device for a specific period
          </li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-custom-dark text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">
          5. Cookie control
        </h2>
        <p class="text-custom-brown">
          You can control and manage cookies in several ways:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc ml-6 mt-2">
          <li>Through your browser settings</li>
          <li>Using our cookie consent banner</li>
          <li>Manually deleting cookies</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-custom-dark text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">
          6. Policy updates
        </h2>
        <p class="text-custom-brown">
          We reserve the right to update this cookie policy at any time. Changes
          will be published on this page.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-custom-dark text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">7. Contact</h2>
        <p class="text-custom-brown">
          If you have any questions about our cookie policy, you can contact us
          at:
        </p>
        <p class="mt-2">Email: contacto@dentalbarcelo.com</p>
        <p class="text-custom-brown">Phone: +34 629 30 00 40</p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>

